    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so if the system is basically just a tool for powerful countries to do whatever they want, isn't it kind of a sham? i mean, if it can't actually protect smaller nations, is it even a legitimate peacekeeping body anymore or is it just a way to make sure the status quo never changes?",
